data.description: BUY THIS AWESOME HOME, WE'LL BUY YOURS!* This AWESOME home shows like new construction! 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout first floor, recessed lighting throughout, open floor plan, cozy family room with fireplace, eat in kitchen with granite countertops and custom backsplash, stainless steel appliances, small center island with additional cabinet space and pantry. Sunroom with vaulted ceiling and french doors that lead out to spacious backyard. Sizable owners suite with walk in closet and private bathroom with stand up shower. So much more to see here! Schedule your private showing today!!
